<type>: <short summary>

# Format:
#   <type>: <short summary>
#
# Examples:
#   feat: add pause menu
#   fix: clamp bot movement to screen bounds
#   docs: update build instructions
#
# Types:
#   feat     - new feature
#   fix      - bug fix
#   docs     - documentation
#   style    - formatting only
#   refactor - code change without behavior change
#   test     - tests
#   build    - build system or dependencies
#   chore    - maintenance
